All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
Command
Command class; contains command values and resolutions that alter the FSM
Command.CommandValue
Enumeration CommandValue containing different commands causing transition in our FSM
Command.Resolution
Enumeration Resolution containing possible resolution types
Issue
Class representing issues to be managed, containing issue ID, summary, owner, confirmed staus, and notes ArrayList
Issue.IssueType
Enumeration for types of issues
IssueList
Class for list of issues being handled by manager.
IssueManager
Issue manager class; manages issues with deletion, addition, saving, and loading functions, as well as command execution
IssueManagerGUI
Container for the IssueManager that has the menu options for new issue files, loading existing files, saving files and quitting.
IssueReader
IO class for reading from files and returning ArrayList of Issues
IssueWriter
IO class in charge of writing issues to files
